snippet.title: Stars Dazzle at Premieres and Gala Events Too - Splash News | Splash News TV | Splash News TV
snippet.description:
Amber Heard and Jessica Chastain brought fashion to the forefront of red carpet events outside of awards shows in a week of high-class style.

Splash is the leading independent entertainment news and picture agency in America.
